00:10:07.228 --> 00:10:08.270 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: And what is it?

00:10:08.270 --> 00:10:11.360 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: I wanted to get the
autistic child all of a sudden

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:14.030 align:middle line:84%
to open up his tension
and see the world the way

00:10:14.030 --> 00:10:16.470 align:middle line:84%
we see it, at least
with an angle.

00:10:16.470 --> 00:10:19.970 align:middle line:84%
People didn't believe that
you could just put an angle

00:10:19.970 --> 00:10:22.430 align:middle line:90%
and change his perceptions.

00:10:22.430 --> 00:10:25.820 align:middle line:84%
And we found that
in by geometry,

00:10:25.820 --> 00:10:32.120 align:middle line:84%
we had patented a shape many
years ago that has to do,

00:10:32.120 --> 00:10:35.060 align:middle line:90%
it's 135 degrees.

00:10:35.060 --> 00:10:41.510 align:middle line:84%
So when you make a
shape of 135 degrees,

00:10:41.510 --> 00:10:43.190 align:middle line:84%
let's say the angle
of an octagon.

00:10:43.190 --> 00:10:44.090 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I was just
going to ask you,

00:10:44.090 --> 00:10:45.290 align:middle line:90%
you were talking octagonal.

00:10:45.290 --> 00:10:45.500 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:10:45.500 --> 00:10:46.300 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Yeah.

00:10:46.300 --> 00:10:47.960 align:middle line:90%
The angle of an octagon.

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:52.700 align:middle line:84%
This is the one that puts
most relaxation in the mind

00:10:52.700 --> 00:10:55.260 align:middle line:84%
of an autistic child
and in a human being.

00:10:55.260 --> 00:10:57.110 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, because
a lot of the sacred,

00:10:57.110 --> 00:11:00.680 align:middle line:84%
like in little temples
and such historically

00:11:00.680 --> 00:11:04.650 align:middle line:84%
have at that center part,
it's octagonal often times.

00:11:04.650 --> 00:11:05.450 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Yeah.

00:11:05.450 --> 00:11:06.830 align:middle line:90%
Even the domes.

00:11:06.830 --> 00:11:09.060 align:middle line:84%
In the domes, when
they come down,

00:11:09.060 --> 00:11:12.938 align:middle line:84%
you will find that they end
up octagonal, square, and all

00:11:12.938 --> 00:11:14.730 align:middle line:84%
that before they end
up in the last shapes.

00:11:14.730 --> 00:11:16.950 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That was like
the last house I lived in.

00:11:16.950 --> 00:11:18.600 align:middle line:90%
Everyone loved being in there.

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:19.490 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Yeah.

00:11:19.490 --> 00:11:24.710 align:middle line:84%
You find that they are corrected
through this transitional shape

00:11:24.710 --> 00:11:25.830 align:middle line:90%
of octagon.

00:11:25.830 --> 00:11:27.710 align:middle line:84%
So the octagon is the
transitional shape

00:11:27.710 --> 00:11:30.030 align:middle line:84%
between the square
and the circle.

00:11:30.030 --> 00:11:34.280 align:middle line:84%
And it is the most,
let's say, relaxing

00:11:34.280 --> 00:11:37.500 align:middle line:90%
shape for the autistic brain.

00:11:37.500 --> 00:11:41.700 align:middle line:84%
But we are all
somehow not normal.

00:11:41.700 --> 00:11:42.500 align:middle line:90%
Who says--

00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:45.000 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: They're just a more
exaggerated version of tension

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:45.857 align:middle line:90%
to what we are.

00:11:45.857 --> 00:11:47.690 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: I don't see
any of us being normal,

00:11:47.690 --> 00:11:50.790 align:middle line:84%
so we all enjoy being
in an octagonal shape.

00:11:50.790 --> 00:11:54.380 align:middle line:84%
What I did was I designed
the project in Egypt

00:11:54.380 --> 00:11:55.760 align:middle line:90%
based on those shapes.

00:11:55.760 --> 00:11:58.460 align:middle line:84%
But you know, to have
the government understand

00:11:58.460 --> 00:12:01.280 align:middle line:84%
what I'm doing because my
geometry seems to many people

00:12:01.280 --> 00:12:06.050 align:middle line:84%
to be a bit strange, I
built an octagonal shape,

00:12:06.050 --> 00:12:10.430 align:middle line:84%
and the roof was sort
of going around up

00:12:10.430 --> 00:12:13.790 align:middle line:84%
like this in a sort of
dome-like structure like this

00:12:13.790 --> 00:12:14.990 align:middle line:90%
with octagons.

00:12:14.990 --> 00:12:18.260 align:middle line:84%
And I told the
centers for autism

00:12:18.260 --> 00:12:21.920 align:middle line:84%
to bring the children with the
doctors and the supervisors,

00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:25.550 align:middle line:84%
and put them in there,
and let them play in there

00:12:25.550 --> 00:12:26.550 align:middle line:90%
and see what happens.

00:12:26.550 --> 00:12:29.940 align:middle line:84%
Because I said the proof in
the cake is in eating it.

00:12:29.940 --> 00:12:31.650 align:middle line:90%
And they brought them there.

00:12:31.650 --> 00:12:34.983 align:middle line:84%
And I can tell you
stories that are endless.

00:12:34.983 --> 00:12:35.900 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Tell us one.

00:12:35.900 --> 00:12:38.790 align:middle line:84%
Just give us an anecdote of
what happened to even one.

00:12:38.790 --> 00:12:41.600 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: Well, I'll give
you two opposite ones.

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:45.410 align:middle line:84%
A child who was hyperactive,
and the instructor

00:12:45.410 --> 00:12:47.880 align:middle line:84%
was holding this little
boy from the hand.

00:12:47.880 --> 00:12:48.810 align:middle line:90%
I said, why hold him?

00:12:48.810 --> 00:12:49.610 align:middle line:90%
Let him play.

00:12:49.610 --> 00:12:52.350 align:middle line:84%
He said, no, if I leave
him, he's going to run.

00:12:52.350 --> 00:12:53.840 align:middle line:90%
We won't be able to catch him.

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:57.140 align:middle line:84%
And before we go to the ship,
the child pulls his hand away,

00:12:57.140 --> 00:12:59.340 align:middle line:84%
keeps running around and
around, and they run after.

00:12:59.340 --> 00:13:00.860 align:middle line:90%
And then they catch him.

00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:03.320 align:middle line:84%
They bring him into
the octagonal shape

00:13:03.320 --> 00:13:04.620 align:middle line:90%
to sit to the others.

00:13:04.620 --> 00:13:06.540 align:middle line:90%
And then there are cubes there.

00:13:06.540 --> 00:13:10.730 align:middle line:84%
So he looks at the cubes, and he
starts playing with the cubes.

00:13:10.730 --> 00:13:15.900 align:middle line:84%
And then after 10 minutes,
he smiles and is happy

00:13:15.900 --> 00:13:19.280 align:middle line:84%
and then goes to one
of the instructors,

00:13:19.280 --> 00:13:23.020 align:middle line:90%
and he sleeps on her lap.

00:13:23.020 --> 00:13:23.918 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Amazing.

00:13:23.918 --> 00:13:24.960 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: And he's asleep.

00:13:24.960 --> 00:13:27.850 align:middle line:84%
Another child who
is autistic and has

00:13:27.850 --> 00:13:30.130 align:middle line:84%
all those tensions and
those cramps and all you

00:13:30.130 --> 00:13:31.630 align:middle line:90%
see with autistic children.

00:13:31.630 --> 00:13:33.220 align:middle line:90%
He goes in there.

00:13:33.220 --> 00:13:37.390 align:middle line:84%
And after 10 minutes,
he starts being normal.

00:13:37.390 --> 00:13:38.870 align:middle line:90%
And he looks at people.

00:13:38.870 --> 00:13:40.400 align:middle line:84%
He sees the world
without tension.

00:13:40.400 --> 00:13:41.600 align:middle line:90%
He's very happy there.

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:43.430 align:middle line:90%
And then he manages.

00:13:43.430 --> 00:13:45.290 align:middle line:84%
There's no spastic
movements and things.

00:13:45.290 --> 00:13:47.030 align:middle line:90%
They all sort of move away.

00:13:47.030 --> 00:13:50.170 align:middle line:84%
Now the mothers told
us that after being

00:13:50.170 --> 00:13:54.040 align:middle line:84%
1.5 hours in the
shape, he went home,

00:13:54.040 --> 00:13:57.310 align:middle line:90%
and he was normal for 24 hours.

00:13:57.310 --> 00:14:00.880 align:middle line:84%
And that's when they
asked me if it's

00:14:00.880 --> 00:14:05.980 align:middle line:84%
possible to design a mini
shape that they could hang up

00:14:05.980 --> 00:14:08.320 align:middle line:84%
in the room of an
autistic child.

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:09.220 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:14:09.220 --> 00:14:10.638 align:middle line:90%
And you.

00:14:10.638 --> 00:14:11.930 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: I designed this shape.

00:14:11.930 --> 00:14:12.730 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:14:12.730 --> 00:14:15.670 align:middle line:84%
We didn't put it
into production yet,

00:14:15.670 --> 00:14:20.380 align:middle line:84%
but we did a lot of testing
with it because if people

00:14:20.380 --> 00:14:24.060 align:middle line:84%
put a lamp inside it or
something like that and use it.

00:14:24.060 --> 00:14:25.880 align:middle line:84%
So we have to do
a lot of testing.

00:14:25.880 --> 00:14:27.990 align:middle line:90%
But we have those shapes.

00:14:27.990 --> 00:14:31.820 align:middle line:90%
We design now carpets, textiles.

00:14:31.820 --> 00:14:36.020 align:middle line:84%
All our products in BioGeometry
now, they have one standard,

00:14:36.020 --> 00:14:39.345 align:middle line:84%
and they have to balance the
mind of an autistic child.

00:14:39.345 --> 00:14:40.145 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:14:40.145 --> 00:14:41.580 align:middle line:90%
So let me ask you this.

00:14:41.580 --> 00:14:45.350 align:middle line:84%
So let's say a person takes
their autistic child home who

00:14:45.350 --> 00:14:48.920 align:middle line:84%
lives in a square room, say
a 12 by 12-foot square room,

00:14:48.920 --> 00:14:56.270 align:middle line:84%
can't you place, for example,
stones into an octagonal

00:14:56.270 --> 00:14:57.350 align:middle line:90%
pattern?

00:14:57.350 --> 00:14:59.150 align:middle line:84%
And can that be set
up where they just

00:14:59.150 --> 00:15:00.380 align:middle line:90%
communicate and create?

00:15:00.380 --> 00:15:01.297 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: It will help.

00:15:01.297 --> 00:15:03.290 align:middle line:90%
It will help if you put--

00:15:03.290 --> 00:15:07.340 align:middle line:84%
you see, you can put things
in the corner one way.

00:15:07.340 --> 00:15:09.230 align:middle line:84%
Just putting anything
in the corner,

00:15:09.230 --> 00:15:11.040 align:middle line:90%
so it will break the corner.

00:15:11.040 --> 00:15:14.760 align:middle line:84%
The child will feel a
bit better in there.

00:15:14.760 --> 00:15:18.980 align:middle line:84%
But when we do
BioGeometry designs,

00:15:18.980 --> 00:15:21.380 align:middle line:90%
we go, of course, much deeper.

00:15:21.380 --> 00:15:25.580 align:middle line:84%
We have courses teaching people
the principles of BioGeometry

00:15:25.580 --> 00:15:26.550 align:middle line:90%
design and all that.

00:15:26.550 --> 00:15:30.800 align:middle line:84%
So it's not just an
octagon because an octagon

00:15:30.800 --> 00:15:34.560 align:middle line:84%
is a fairly stable
shape like that.

00:15:34.560 --> 00:15:35.360 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:15:35.360 --> 00:15:38.360 align:middle line:84%
We put some dynamic
action into it.

00:15:38.360 --> 00:15:42.230 align:middle line:84%
You know, like you have
the teepees of the Indians.

00:15:42.230 --> 00:15:44.120 align:middle line:90%
Many of them are octagonal.

00:15:44.120 --> 00:15:49.340 align:middle line:84%
But the way those
poles come up together,

00:15:49.340 --> 00:15:51.510 align:middle line:84%
they create a sort
of rotation a bit.

00:15:51.510 --> 00:15:52.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:15:52.310 --> 00:15:55.820 align:middle line:84%
They're slightly,
like they're twisting.

00:15:55.820 --> 00:15:58.410 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: So you can't say
that the teepee is an octagon.

00:15:58.410 --> 00:15:59.210 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:15:59.210 --> 00:16:00.705 align:middle line:90%
It is actually creating--

00:16:00.705 --> 00:16:02.580 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: A movement,
an octagon in movement.

00:16:02.580 --> 00:16:03.380 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Yeah.

00:16:03.380 --> 00:16:07.185 align:middle line:84%
And this movement sort of clears
your brain, and your energy,

00:16:07.185 --> 00:16:08.060 align:middle line:90%
and things like that.

00:16:08.060 --> 00:16:08.160 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:09.890 align:middle line:84%
So while we're on
this roll then,

00:16:09.890 --> 00:16:12.050 align:middle line:84%
a lot of people
watching this right now

00:16:12.050 --> 00:16:14.760 align:middle line:84%
are very connected to
having personal pyramids,

00:16:14.760 --> 00:16:16.160 align:middle line:90%
going to the pyramids.

00:16:16.160 --> 00:16:18.750 align:middle line:84%
And your background,
of course, is Egyptian.

00:16:18.750 --> 00:16:20.810 align:middle line:84%
You understand the nature
of these pyramids well.

00:16:20.810 --> 00:16:24.140 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about what
happens when you go into

00:16:24.140 --> 00:16:27.410 align:middle line:84%
or when you sit-in front
of a pyramidal structure

00:16:27.410 --> 00:16:29.520 align:middle line:84%
and what that
should be used for.

00:16:29.520 --> 00:16:33.200 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: Well, let's start,
what's a pyramidal structure?

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:36.560 align:middle line:84%
A pyramidal structure
is the last stage

00:16:36.560 --> 00:16:41.852 align:middle line:84%
of how humanity interacted
with sacred power spots.

00:16:41.852 --> 00:16:43.060 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Sacred power spots.

00:16:43.060 --> 00:16:43.190 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:16:43.190 --> 00:16:44.390 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Sacred power spots.

00:16:44.390 --> 00:16:46.220 align:middle line:84%
At the dawn of
humanity, they used

00:16:46.220 --> 00:16:48.800 align:middle line:84%
to watch animals go
to sacred power spots

00:16:48.800 --> 00:16:51.290 align:middle line:84%
because they had sacred
springs or water.

00:16:51.290 --> 00:16:52.850 align:middle line:90%
So humans used to go there.

00:16:52.850 --> 00:16:54.800 align:middle line:84%
And then they start
in the beginning

00:16:54.800 --> 00:16:59.840 align:middle line:84%
of feeling this energy because
they were more right-brained,

00:16:59.840 --> 00:17:01.050 align:middle line:90%
like animals and all that.

00:17:01.050 --> 00:17:03.750 align:middle line:84%
So they saw the
light in those areas.

00:17:03.750 --> 00:17:07.593 align:middle line:84%
And then what they did,
they brought huge granite--

00:17:07.593 --> 00:17:08.510 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, stones.

00:17:08.510 --> 00:17:09.310 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Stones.

00:17:09.310 --> 00:17:12.260 align:middle line:84%
Because granite has
quartz crystals.

00:17:12.260 --> 00:17:15.650 align:middle line:84%
And they would radiate the
energy of the sacred power spots

00:17:15.650 --> 00:17:17.520 align:middle line:90%
to larger areas.

00:17:17.520 --> 00:17:19.460 align:middle line:84%
So the whole community
living around it

00:17:19.460 --> 00:17:22.500 align:middle line:90%
would benefit from this energy.

00:17:22.500 --> 00:17:24.109 align:middle line:84%
And then they found
also that if they

00:17:24.109 --> 00:17:27.960 align:middle line:84%
pointed at it from a distance,
somehow they got the light.

00:17:27.960 --> 00:17:32.790 align:middle line:84%
So rituals were developed in
relation to sacred power spots.

00:17:32.790 --> 00:17:38.940 align:middle line:84%
Now the second thing they did,
which shows a lot of knowledge,

00:17:38.940 --> 00:17:44.730 align:middle line:84%
they erected two megalithic
stones and one across.

00:17:44.730 --> 00:17:47.700 align:middle line:90%
Imagine each one is 40 tons.

00:17:47.700 --> 00:17:49.120 align:middle line:90%
So they did that.

00:17:49.120 --> 00:17:53.730 align:middle line:84%
But the thing is they
always pointed the opening

00:17:53.730 --> 00:17:55.420 align:middle line:90%
to the equinoxes, east-west.

00:17:55.420 --> 00:17:56.220 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:17:56.220 --> 00:18:00.570 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: Now I want
to measure why that?

00:18:00.570 --> 00:18:03.150 align:middle line:84%
I found when you take two
shapes and you point them

00:18:03.150 --> 00:18:04.830 align:middle line:84%
in this direction,
all of a sudden,

00:18:04.830 --> 00:18:06.840 align:middle line:84%
the sacred energy
of the power spots

00:18:06.840 --> 00:18:13.070 align:middle line:84%
shoots all the way to both
equinoxes, to the east and west.

00:18:13.070 --> 00:18:17.050 align:middle line:84%
That means it then connects
to the cycle of life.

00:18:17.050 --> 00:18:20.450 align:middle line:84%
So you're connecting the sacred
power spot to the cycle of life

00:18:20.450 --> 00:18:25.190 align:middle line:84%
through a gateway that
we call now the dolmen.

00:18:25.190 --> 00:18:30.950 align:middle line:84%
Then they came later and
put on it, they put earth.

00:18:30.950 --> 00:18:34.120 align:middle line:84%
So it became a
chamber in a mound.

00:18:34.120 --> 00:18:35.730 align:middle line:90%
So that is the sacred mound.

00:18:35.730 --> 00:18:37.647 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And that's
what most people watching

00:18:37.647 --> 00:18:41.370 align:middle line:84%
this know of dolmens, are these
sacred domes around the world.

00:18:41.370 --> 00:18:43.618 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: Well, first, now
it's just an earth mound.

00:18:43.618 --> 00:18:44.910 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah, an earth mound.

00:18:44.910 --> 00:18:50.760 align:middle line:84%
>>KARIM: And then later on,
the mound becomes a pyramid.

00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:56.360 align:middle line:84%
And so the pyramid is
actually, the chamber in there

00:18:56.360 --> 00:19:00.620 align:middle line:84%
is a dolmen connecting
the cycle of life

00:19:00.620 --> 00:19:04.610 align:middle line:84%
and basically connecting
with the life force

00:19:04.610 --> 00:19:09.410 align:middle line:84%
because the sacred
power spot is results

00:19:09.410 --> 00:19:18.030 align:middle line:84%
from an intersection of two,
let's say, underwater currents,

00:19:18.030 --> 00:19:19.560 align:middle line:90%
but not any water.

00:19:19.560 --> 00:19:21.600 align:middle line:90%
Water moving in the rocks.

00:19:21.600 --> 00:19:24.940 align:middle line:84%
This is a very special kind of
water that moves in the rocks.

00:19:24.940 --> 00:19:28.140 align:middle line:84%
And when they cross,
they create a vortex.

00:19:28.140 --> 00:19:30.510 align:middle line:84%
Now when they
create this vortex,

00:19:30.510 --> 00:19:32.710 align:middle line:90%
what happens with this water?

00:19:32.710 --> 00:19:37.140 align:middle line:84%
It connects physical
water through resonance

00:19:37.140 --> 00:19:40.950 align:middle line:84%
to the primordial ocean or
the primordial dimension.

00:19:40.950 --> 00:19:43.950 align:middle line:84%
So you get a sacred
power spot that

00:19:43.950 --> 00:19:51.040 align:middle line:84%
takes you multidimensionally
up even beyond duality.

00:19:51.040 --> 00:19:52.890 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So what
happens then now

00:19:52.890 --> 00:19:55.890 align:middle line:84%
when the Egyptians and other
cultures around the world,

00:19:55.890 --> 00:19:59.850 align:middle line:84%
Central, South America, and on,
and on started creating then,

00:19:59.850 --> 00:20:03.780 align:middle line:84%
you have the initial
structure, and then they

