00:40:44.740 --> 00:40:46.330 align:middle line:84%
It's a way of
understanding things.

00:40:46.330 --> 00:40:51.840 align:middle line:84%
But if you just go into
multidimensional time,

00:40:51.840 --> 00:40:53.700 align:middle line:90%
stop for a moment.

00:40:53.700 --> 00:40:56.820 align:middle line:84%
If you stop for a
moment, then karma

00:40:56.820 --> 00:40:59.623 align:middle line:84%
will have difficulty
dealing with you.

00:40:59.623 --> 00:41:00.540 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Interesting.

00:41:00.540 --> 00:41:01.340 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Yes.

00:41:01.340 --> 00:41:05.190 align:middle line:84%
Because how will it deal
with somebody who is just,

00:41:05.190 --> 00:41:06.190 align:middle line:90%
there's a circle.

00:41:06.190 --> 00:41:07.830 align:middle line:84%
You're walking
around the circle.

00:41:07.830 --> 00:41:10.660 align:middle line:90%
So I know where to catch you.

00:41:10.660 --> 00:41:11.460 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:41:11.460 --> 00:41:12.600 align:middle line:90%
That's with karma.

00:41:12.600 --> 00:41:14.850 align:middle line:84%
