00:41:16.940 --> 00:41:19.100 align:middle line:84%
So I don't see on
the circle anymore.

00:41:19.100 --> 00:41:20.180 align:middle line:90%
You're not here.

00:41:20.180 --> 00:41:21.870 align:middle line:90%
So I can't affect you anymore.

00:41:21.870 --> 00:41:24.020 align:middle line:84%
And then when you decide
to come out again,

00:41:24.020 --> 00:41:27.450 align:middle line:84%
you come out in the
direction you want,

00:41:27.450 --> 00:41:28.658 align:middle line:90%
and nothing has affected you.

00:41:28.658 --> 00:41:31.117 align:middle line:84%
