not maybe the best way for you

00:41:46.920 --> 00:41:47.910 align:middle line:90%
to go anymore.

00:41:47.910 --> 00:41:50.080 align:middle line:90%
So you pause.

00:41:50.080 --> 00:41:54.260 align:middle line:84%
