aggressive tendency happens.

00:41:54.260 --> 00:41:55.260 align:middle line:90%
Stop.

00:41:55.260 --> 00:41:56.260 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: And then think.

00:41:56.260 --> 00:41:58.630 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Allow the
life force to come in.

00:41:58.630 --> 00:41:59.900 align:middle line:90%
Go into the other space maybe.

00:41:59.900 --> 00:42:00.700 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Yes.

00:42:00.700 --> 00:42:03.610 align:middle line:90%
Think with that person.

00:42:03.610 --> 00:42:07.870 align:middle line:84%
Let's say a person is very
strong and very aggressive.

00:42:07.870 --> 00:42:12.440 align:middle line:84%
Now if I stop and
not do anything,

00:42:12.440 --> 00:42:14.690 align:middle line:84%
that person didn't
learn a lesson.

00:42:14.690 --> 00:42:17.280 align:middle line:84%
Because he knows he's
an aggressive person.

00:42:17.280 --> 00:42:20.210 align:middle line:90%
He expects me not to react.

00:42:20.210 --> 00:42:24.080 align:middle line:84%
