I should be aggressive

00:42:26.210 --> 00:42:28.940 align:middle line:84%
because he doesn't
expect it, and this

00:42:28.940 --> 00:42:30.460 align:middle line:90%
is what will change him.

00:42:30.460 --> 00:42:32.810 align:middle line:90%
Now we come to a weak person.

00:42:32.810 --> 00:42:35.870 align:middle line:84%
Everybody is hitting them on
the head, this weak person.

00:42:35.870 --> 00:42:37.140 align:middle line:90%
