00:42:37.140 --> 00:42:40.852 align:middle line:84%
So all of a sudden,
you decide, no.

00:42:40.852 --> 00:42:42.560 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Let me be
gentle and let them--

00:42:42.560 --> 00:42:43.360 align:middle line:90%
>>KARIM: Yeah.

00:42:43.360 --> 00:42:45.550 align:middle line:84%
So he will all of a sudden
look at you and say,

00:42:45.550 --> 00:42:46.910 align:middle line:90%
