00:42:51.140 --> 00:42:54.800 align:middle line:84%
So that you bring in the wisdom
from the multidimensionality

00:42:54.800 --> 00:42:55.600 align:middle line:90%
in that.

00:42:55.600 --> 00:42:56.950 align:middle line:90%
But remember--

00:42:56.950 --> 00:43:00.130 align:middle line:84%
